Description:
The Hunter Irrigation Short Radius Micro Spray Nozzles are the perfect solution for irrigating small or intricate spaces with precision and efficiency. Designed specifically for compact areas, these highly accurate nozzles deliver targeted water distribution, making them ideal for gardens, flower beds, or tight landscaping zones. When paired with Pro-Spray pop-ups, they create a robust micro-spray system that ensures reliable performance and even coverage. The short radius design minimizes over-spray and water waste, while their durable construction ensures long-lasting use in various weather conditions. Easy to install and maintain, these micro spray nozzles are a smart choice for anyone looking to optimize irrigation in smaller spaces without compromising on quality or efficiency. Upgrade your irrigation system with Hunter's Short Radius Micro Spray Nozzles for precise, water-saving performance in every corner of your landscape.

For controlled irrigation of small spaces, Hunter offers a complete line of short-radius micro spray nozzles. The ASABE/ICC 802-2014 standard defines a micro spray as an emission device with a flow rate of 30 GPH or less at the largest area of coverage available when operated at 30 PSI. As landscaped areas continue to shrink in size, short radius micro spray nozzles provide an accurate watering solution for 2', 4', and 6' spaces while supporting a robust micro spray system.

&nbsp;

